title: Taylor Swift celebrates 50m Instagram followers
text:
Taylor Swift celebrates 50m Instagram followers 11th Oct 2015 6:00 AM Cars For Sale 
TAYLOR Swift is celebrating 50 million Instagram followers. 
The 'Shake It Off' hitmaker is the first person to reach the milestone, with Kim Kardashian West and Beyonc√© following close behind with 48.4 million and 47.5 million followers respectively. 
However, Taylor claims she only got the accolade because she has "cute cats". 
Sharing a screenshot of her profile, she wrote: "50 million followers! Thanks so much guys. I'm pretty sure this is just because I have cute cats though. (sic)" 
And despite her 50 million followers not being able to get enough of her, the 25-year-old beauty recently admitted she feels as though people "need a break" from her. 
She shared: "I think I should take some time off. People might need a break from me. I'm going to hang out with friends. Write new music. Maybe not write new music. I don't know. 
"If you let your anxiety get the better of you, like everybody's waiting for you to really mess up, then you'll be done. A lot of the time I call my mom and talk for a really long time, just to remind myself of all the things that are great and that matter." bang showbiz
